<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3341] Kafka connector&apos;s &apos;auto.offset.reset&apos; inconsistent with Kafka</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3341</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Kafka docs talk of valid &quot;auto.offset.reset&quot; values being &quot;smallest&quot; or &quot;largest&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://kafka.apache.org/08/configuration.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://kafka.apache.org/08/configuration.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;LegacyFetcher&lt;/tt&gt; looks for &quot;latest&quot; and otherwise defaults to &quot;smallest&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=rmetzger&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;rmetzger&quot;&gt;rmetzger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
